headline: 1 Magnificent Dividend Stock Down 15% to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: Global trade is being disrupted, but new trade lines will likely form.  Prologis' stock price has fallen amid the uncertainty, but its global portfolio positions it well for the future.  The United States has taken an aggressive stand with regard to tariffs.
